<note n="0300c1701" resp="#resp2" type="add" target="#nkr_note_add_0300c1701"><g ref="#RJ-C963">􌥣</g>【CB】，<g ref="#RJ-E060">􎁠</g>【卍續】</note>
<note n="0300c1801" resp="#resp2" type="add" target="#nkr_note_add_0300c1801">但【CB】，伹【卍續】</note>
<note n="0300c2101" resp="#resp2" type="add" target="#nkr_note_add_0300c2101">已【CB】，巳【卍續】</note>
